01:00:18.882 --> 01:00:20.349
(Frances) You can't handle real life?

01:00:20.351 --> 01:00:23.018
You don't have the guts to be like us.

01:00:23.020 --> 01:00:24.152
Frances, stop!

01:00:24.154 --> 01:00:26.355
You don't know anything.

01:00:26.357 --> 01:00:29.024
Is bitch-boy gonna cry?

01:00:29.026 --> 01:00:31.226
Cry like a baby!

01:00:31.228 --> 01:00:32.928
Or do you only do that for Jamie?

01:00:32.930 --> 01:00:34.196
Don't listen to her, Adam.

01:00:34.198 --> 01:00:36.331
- Is that it?
- Shut up.

01:00:36.333 --> 01:00:37.633
(Jamie) Adam, let's go.

01:00:37.635 --> 01:00:38.934
You just can't stand the heat.

01:00:38.936 --> 01:00:40.936
Maybe you should take your dead boyfriend

01:00:40.938 --> 01:00:45.007
