01:00:45.775 --> 01:00:47.776
(Jamie) Adam, let's go, please!

01:00:47.778 --> 01:00:49.678
(Adam) I'll show you heat.

01:00:49.680 --> 01:00:51.046
Adam, what are you doing?!

01:00:51.048 --> 01:00:52.781
- Fuck you, Frances!
- No!

01:00:52.783 --> 01:00:54.349
We don't need your shit!

01:00:54.351 --> 01:00:57.986
- Oh, my God.
- Let's go.

01:00:57.988 --> 01:00:59.388
Oh, my God.

01:00:59.390 --> 01:01:01.790
You shouldn't have done this, Adam.

01:01:01.792 --> 01:01:02.891
(Frances) What did you do?

01:01:02.893 --> 01:01:04.693
You shouldn't have done this.

01:01:04.695 --> 01:01:05.827
This is mine!

01:01:05.829 --> 01:01:07.863
This is my house!

01:01:07.865 --> 01:01:11.767
No, no, no, no, no!

01:01:11.769 --> 01:01:14.336
No, no!

01:01:15.038 --> 01:01:18.273
You motherfucking cocksucker!

01:01:18.275 --> 01:01:20.208
You're a fucking cocksucker!

01:01:20.210 --> 01:01:22.210
This is mine!

01:01:22.212 --> 01:01:23.945
Mine!

01:01:23.947 --> 01:01:26.314
No, no!

01:01:36.125 --> 01:01:38.827
(Jamie) Run!

01:01:38.829 --> 01:01:40.395
Go!

01:01:43.299 --> 01:01:47.235
(Frances screaming)

01:01:50.740 --> 01:01:53.842
(Jamie) Go, Adam, go!

01:01:53.844 --> 01:01:55.911
Jamie!

01:01:55.913 --> 01:01:58.080
(Frances) Get off me!

01:01:58.082 --> 01:01:59.748
Get off me!

01:01:59.750 --> 01:02:02.384
Get out of here!

01:02:39.222 --> 01:02:43.024
(Muffled) Are you okay, kid?

01:02:43.026 --> 01:02:44.493
How much?

01:02:44.495 --> 01:02:47.229
Three dollars.

01:02:58.074 --> 01:03:00.509
Change?

01:03:00.511 --> 01:03:03.011
No.

01:03:19.962 --> 01:03:23.165
<i>(Line ringing)</i>

01:03:24.801 --> 01:03:27.936
<i>(Gracie) Hello?</i>

01:03:27.938 --> 01:03:31.907
- Hi.
- <i>Adam?</i>

01:03:31.909 --> 01:03:34.209
<i>What's going on?</i>

01:03:34.211 --> 01:03:37.979
I burned down the Wilkinson farm.

01:03:40.583 --> 01:03:42.584
<i>Where are you?</i>

01:03:42.586 --> 01:03:45.987
Behind the old Apollo.

01:03:45.989 --> 01:03:48.590
<i>How glamorous.</i>

01:03:48.592 --> 01:03:51.493
<i>Is he there with you?</i>

01:03:51.495 --> 01:03:54.129
No.

01:03:54.131 --> 01:03:56.164
He's mad at me.

01:03:56.166 --> 01:03:59.034
I don't know where he is.

01:03:59.036 --> 01:04:01.837
<i>Are you lying to me?</i>

01:04:02.872 --> 01:04:05.373
No, Gracie, I'm not lying to you.

01:04:05.375 --> 01:04:06.942
I don't know where he is.

01:04:06.944 --> 01:04:08.410
Look...

01:04:08.412 --> 01:04:09.244
I think I have to go.

01:04:09.246 --> 01:04:11.313
<i>Adam, don't go anywhere, okay?</i>

01:04:11.315 --> 01:04:13.982
<i>- I’ll be there as soon as...</i>
- No, Gracie, listen to me,

01:04:13.984 --> 01:04:17.118
