- <i>(Dial tone)</i>

01:04:36.138 --> 01:04:39.174
I'm not mad at you, Adam.

01:04:42.511 --> 01:04:45.113
I'm just disappointed.

01:04:48.384 --> 01:04:51.253
You shouldn't have done that.

01:04:51.255 --> 01:04:53.622
You had no right.

01:04:55.258 --> 01:04:57.259
I know.

01:04:59.028 --> 01:05:01.563
I'm sorry.

01:05:05.468 --> 01:05:09.938
You wouldn't do anything like that to me, would you?

01:05:17.313 --> 01:05:20.115
Of course you wouldn't.

01:05:43.272 --> 01:05:47.008
(Footsteps approaching)

01:05:58.387 --> 01:06:02.724
