01:06:57.580 --> 01:07:00.782
Why were you running away from me?

01:07:00.784 --> 01:07:02.017
I wasn't running away from you,

01:07:02.019 --> 01:07:06.121
I was just... I was just running.

01:07:12.628 --> 01:07:15.163
What was that place?

01:07:15.464 --> 01:07:18.666
Were those people all dead?

01:07:20.269 --> 01:07:23.405
Don't worry about them, Adam.

01:07:27.343 --> 01:07:28.410
If I could see them,

01:07:28.412 --> 01:07:31.813
does that mean they could see me?

01:07:31.815 --> 01:07:33.281
Huh?

01:07:33.283 --> 01:07:36.718
I would never let them hurt you, Adam.

01:07:44.293 --> 01:07:46.528
Come on.

01:07:46.530 --> 01:07:49.364
I'll make you a fire.

01:08:24.166 --> 01:08:27.801
Jamie, where's Frances?

01:08:31.607 --> 01:08:34.676
Don't worry about her.

01:08:36.578 --> 01:08:39.481
I'm protecting you.

01:08:42.484 --> 01:08:45.653
♪♪

01:09:34.904 --> 01:09:38.305
Are you okay?

01:09:38.308 --> 01:09:42.477
(Breathing heavily)

01:09:43.746 --> 01:09:46.948
Maybe you should just come home.

01:09:48.617 --> 01:09:49.484
No.

01:09:49.486 --> 01:09:53.220
You can't just hide out forever.

01:09:58.894 --> 01:10:01.563
I know that.

01:10:09.538 --> 01:10:12.607
What was she like?

01:10:12.609 --> 01:10:14.876
Awful.

01:10:15.277 --> 01:10:18.913
Her parents were there too.

01:10:18.915 --> 01:10:20.815
She'd kill them...

01:10:20.817 --> 01:10:25.553
every morning, over and over.

01:10:25.555 --> 01:10:26.454
Poor thing.

01:10:26.456 --> 01:10:28.289
She's not a poor thing!

01:10:28.291 --> 01:10:32.360
She's a fucking psychopath bitch that attacked me.

01:10:32.362 --> 01:10:35.830
Don't get all compassionate all of a sudden.

01:10:35.832 --> 01:10:37.665
It's why we're here in the first place.

01:10:37.667 --> 01:10:39.934
Yeah, well, I would be a bitch too

01:10:39.936 --> 01:10:43.004
if I had to kill my parents over and over again

01:10:43.006 --> 01:10:46.407
every morning for all of eternity.

01:10:54.316 --> 01:10:56.451
You know, none of this would have ever happened

01:10:56.453 --> 01:10:57.652
if you had just listened to me

01:10:57.654 --> 01:11:01.723
and stayed the fuck away from Mooney Marks.

01:11:12.034 --> 01:11:12.900
I really should go.

01:11:12.902 --> 01:11:15.436
I don't want you to get in any more trouble than you are.

01:11:15.438 --> 01:11:18.473
But this... it's fine, Adam.

01:11:18.475 --> 01:11:21.442
I brought you some things.

01:11:21.444 --> 01:11:25.346
Just a pillow, some food.

01:11:27.416 --> 01:11:29.350
You didn't have to.

01:11:29.352 --> 01:11:31.953
I know.

01:11:31.955 --> 01:11:34.522
(Door closes)
Adam?

01:11:38.627 --> 01:11:41.763
I think that I love you.

01:11:41.765 --> 01:11:45.633
And I just wanted you to know that.

01:11:49.038 --> 01:11:50.738
♪♪

01:11:50.740 --> 01:11:53.508
Thanks.

01:12:21.036 --> 01:12:23.471
I like it here.

01:12:23.473 --> 01:12:26.107
Just me and you.

01:12:26.575 --> 01:12:29.777
We could stay like this forever.

01:12:47.763 --> 01:12:52.467
<i>(Echoing police-radio chatter)</i>

01:12:52.469 --> 01:12:55.103
(Pounding)

01:12:55.105 --> 01:12:58.639
<i>(Police-radio chatter)</i>

01:13:24.833 --> 01:13:28.069
(Linda) Come here.

01:13:36.879 --> 01:13:40.681
Don't you ever do that again.

01:14:00.836 --> 01:14:02.804
<i>(Man on TV) ...The tropical and pristine</i>

01:14:02.806 --> 01:14:05.006
<i>- coast of Belize.</i>
<i>- (Woman on TV) Wow!</i>

01:14:05.008 --> 01:14:06.474
<i>A visit to this tiny country</i>

01:14:06.476 --> 01:14:08.609
<i>at the northern tip of Central America</i>

01:14:08.611 --> 01:14:11.612
<i>is a magnificent visit back in time.</i>

01:14:11.614 --> 01:14:13.614
<i>You'll see ancient Mayan ruins,</i>

01:14:13.616 --> 01:14:16.918
<i>second only in size to the great pyramids of Egypt.</i>

01:14:16.920 --> 01:14:18.486
<i>Or spend the day island hopping.</i>

01:14:18.488 --> 01:14:19.120
(Adam) Mom?

01:14:19.122 --> 01:14:22.857
<i>(Man on TV) On one of the hundreds of tiny tropical islands...</i>

01:14:22.859 --> 01:14:25.760
(Dog barking)

01:14:25.762 --> 01:14:27.228
<i>(Woman on TV) ...Is second only in size</i>

01:14:27.230 --> 01:14:30.698
<i>to the great barrier reef off Australia.</i>

01:14:30.700 --> 01:14:31.232
<i>Absolutely.</i>

01:14:31.234 --> 01:14:33.201
<i>It's really a spectacular trip.</i>

01:14:33.203 --> 01:14:35.136
<i>Next, you'll wave goodbye to Belize</i>

01:14:35.138 --> 01:14:38.506
<i>as we set sail for the undiscovered jewel</i>

01:14:38.508 --> 01:14:39.607
<i>of the Caribbean,</i>

01:14:39.609 --> 01:14:41.642
<i>Roatan Island, Honduras.</i>

01:14:41.644 --> 01:14:43.044
<i>Sounds like an adventure.</i>

01:14:43.046 --> 01:14:43.878
<i>Oh, it is, Janet.</i>

01:14:43.880 --> 01:14:47.181
<i>This is truly one of the most untouched and beautiful islands</i>

01:14:47.183 --> 01:14:48.516
<i>on the planet.</i>

01:14:48.518 --> 01:14:49.217
Jamie?

01:14:49.219 --> 01:14:51.853
<i>(TV chatter continues)</i>

01:14:51.855 --> 01:14:53.020
Jamie, is that you?

01:14:53.022 --> 01:14:56.858
(Frances) You wish.

01:14:56.860 --> 01:14:57.758
Frances.

01:14:57.760 --> 01:14:59.494
(Match striking)

01:15:02.030 --> 01:15:05.032
Don't be scared.

01:15:07.169 --> 01:15:09.737
- What do you want?
- You owe me, Adam.

01:15:09.739 --> 01:15:12.507
(Match striking)

01:15:12.509 --> 01:15:15.710
It was an accident, Frances.

01:15:15.712 --> 01:15:16.177
I swear.

01:15:16.179 --> 01:15:18.713
And if you think for a second...

01:15:18.715 --> 01:15:19.247
(Match striking)

01:15:19.249 --> 01:15:20.948
...I'm letting you get away with it,

01:15:20.950 --> 01:15:25.653
then you're really as pathetic as I thought you were.

01:15:27.289 --> 01:15:30.691
(Match striking)

01:15:30.693 --> 01:15:33.995
Maybe I'll burn down your house.

01:15:33.997 --> 01:15:35.062
Burn your mom

01:15:35.064 --> 01:15:40.301
as she tries to climb out of the bed into the chair.

01:15:47.109 --> 01:15:51.812
You're not so brave without your little boy-toy.

01:16:00.155 --> 01:16:02.323
(Match striking)

01:16:05.594 --> 01:16:07.929
Adam...

01:16:10.999 --> 01:16:12.333
(Knife scraping against door)

01:16:12.335 --> 01:16:15.002
Open the door.

01:16:25.180 --> 01:16:26.314
Adam...

01:16:26.316 --> 01:16:29.617
Open the door.

01:16:38.360 --> 01:16:40.861
Open the door!

01:16:40.863 --> 01:16:42.196
(Frances growling)

01:16:42.198 --> 01:16:46.033
- Shit.
- Open the door, Adam!

01:16:50.205 --> 01:16:52.907
(Frances screaming)

01:16:52.909 --> 01:16:56.210
(Pounding on door)

01:17:06.855 --> 01:17:11.058
(Adam) Jamie, Jamie, Jamie!

01:17:39.721 --> 01:17:41.822
Oh, how nice.

01:17:41.824 --> 01:17:45.960
Your dead boyfriend to the rescue.

01:17:47.029 --> 01:17:50.364
He thinks you're gonna save him.

01:17:50.366 --> 01:17:55.269
Did you not forget he's more like me than you?

01:17:55.271 --> 01:17:57.872
Leave him alone.

01:17:57.874 --> 01:18:01.208
He's not yours.

01:18:01.210 --> 01:18:04.011
So he's yours?

01:18:05.080 --> 01:18:08.883
Adam?

01:18:08.885 --> 01:18:10.117
I'm his.

01:18:10.119 --> 01:18:13.754
You little bitch-boy.

01:18:16.224 --> 01:18:19.460
Just give me the knife.

01:18:19.462 --> 01:18:21.295
You can't stay here.

01:18:21.297 --> 01:18:22.897
Says who?

01:18:22.899 --> 01:18:24.098
It's just done, you know that.

01:18:24.100 --> 01:18:26.100
Don't tell me what I know!

01:18:26.102 --> 01:18:27.435
I know a fuck a lot more than you,

01:18:27.437 --> 01:18:31.305
and if he hadn't come, I wouldn't be here.

01:18:31.307 --> 01:18:34.809
It doesn't change anything.

01:18:36.812 --> 01:18:40.047
You still have to go.

01:18:47.389 --> 01:18:50.758
(Sobbing)

01:19:00.402 --> 01:19:04.338
I'm so... Jamie, I'm sorry.

01:19:09.945 --> 01:19:12.146
It's okay.

01:19:14.750 --> 01:19:17.184
I'll take you home.

01:19:21.757 --> 01:19:25.092
Get out of there, Adam.

01:19:25.094 --> 01:19:29.096
(Frances sniffling)

01:20:09.037 --> 01:20:12.573
(Indistinct shouting)

01:20:41.269 --> 01:20:42.436
(Jamie) You know you're lucky

01:20:42.438 --> 01:20:46.407
I didn't let her rip your heart out.

01:20:46.409 --> 01:20:47.842
That's what she wanted to do.

01:20:47.844 --> 01:20:50.144
Stop sneaking up on me like that.

01:20:50.146 --> 01:20:52.947
Don't snap at me.

01:20:52.949 --> 01:20:56.483
I'm not snapping.

01:20:56.485 --> 01:20:59.320
Where did you take her?

01:20:59.322 --> 01:21:01.622
Doesn't matter.

01:21:03.491 --> 01:21:06.594
Was it to that tunnel?

01:21:11.199 --> 01:21:14.935
What happens if you don't go?

01:21:17.539 --> 01:21:21.308
I would never do that to you, Adam.

01:21:22.244 --> 01:21:27.014
Not now that we've found each other.

01:22:04.219 --> 01:22:07.922
Can I have some more, Adam?

01:22:11.593 --> 01:22:14.194
More what?

01:22:17.365 --> 01:22:20.034
Words.

01:22:39.454 --> 01:22:41.956
Close your eyes.

01:22:55.737 --> 01:22:58.572
I'm ready.

01:23:03.611 --> 01:23:05.245
Butterfly.

01:23:05.247 --> 01:23:06.747
In my mouth.

01:23:06.749 --> 01:23:10.084
Say them in my mouth.

01:23:19.694 --> 01:23:21.996
Butterfly.

01:23:21.998 --> 01:23:23.630
More.

01:23:23.632 --> 01:23:24.498
More.

01:23:24.500 --> 01:23:26.133
Pollywog.

01:23:26.135 --> 01:23:27.101
Popsicle.

01:23:27.103 --> 01:23:30.437
- Sunflower.
- (Sobbing)

01:23:45.253 --> 01:23:48.522
You still see me, Adam, don't you?

01:23:53.128 --> 01:23:53.761
I still see you.

01:23:53.763 --> 01:23:58.132
(Aaron) Who the fuck are you talking to?

01:23:58.134 --> 01:24:00.300
No one.

01:24:00.302 --> 01:24:04.304
You really are bat-shit crazy, huh?

01:24:04.306 --> 01:24:07.074
Looks like you're famous.

01:24:07.076 --> 01:24:10.344
For being a freak.

01:24:20.522 --> 01:24:24.425
You look happy in that picture.

01:24:24.427 --> 01:24:28.162
Why don't you look happy now?

01:24:31.833 --> 01:24:35.602
You're not gonna leave me, Adam, are you?

01:24:36.805 --> 01:24:39.840
Not like everyone else.

01:24:43.445 --> 01:24:47.281
Promise... promise me.

01:24:51.553 --> 01:24:54.688
I need you to say it.

01:24:57.792 --> 01:25:00.627
I promise.

01:25:03.198 --> 01:25:07.734
(Window tapping)

01:25:16.478 --> 01:25:19.513
What time is it?

01:25:19.515 --> 01:25:22.449
Can we talk, please?

01:25:28.790 --> 01:25:31.158
My parents caught me sneaking out to see you,

01:25:31.160 --> 01:25:34.428
and I didn't know what else to do.

01:25:35.597 --> 01:25:38.499
I'm sorry about earlier.

01:25:38.501 --> 01:25:41.268
About everything.

01:25:43.671 --> 01:25:47.307
I didn't tell them about the fire.

01:25:49.511 --> 01:25:52.713
I thought I could fix things.

01:25:52.715 --> 01:25:54.448
You know, make it better somehow.

01:25:54.450 --> 01:25:55.415
I... I should've listened.

01:25:55.417 --> 01:25:57.885
I should've, but everything's just getting worse.

01:25:57.887 --> 01:25:59.486
Hey.

01:25:59.488 --> 01:26:00.854
I don't know what to do.

01:26:00.856 --> 01:26:02.556
Adam.

01:26:02.558 --> 01:26:06.493
I have something you should see.

01:26:22.810 --> 01:26:24.411
What is this?

01:26:24.413 --> 01:26:27.214
Just read it.

01:26:29.684 --> 01:26:33.420
"Things I'd Like to Kill.”

01:26:33.422 --> 01:26:34.521
"My mother's ceramic nativity

01:26:34.523 --> 01:26:37.324
"that she keeps out all fucking year long,

01:26:37.326 --> 01:26:40.327
Artie Chapman's plastered on smile."

01:26:40.329 --> 01:26:42.462
Where'd you find this?

01:26:42.464 --> 01:26:45.599
He had it when I found him.

01:26:45.601 --> 01:26:46.466
Just keep reading.

01:26:46.468 --> 01:26:48.635
"My father, wherever he is,

01:26:48.637 --> 01:26:51.872
"Matt Harden and the entire varsity team,

01:26:51.874 --> 01:26:53.407
"except for...

01:26:53.409 --> 01:26:57.277
“Adam McCormick, of course.

01:27:03.718 --> 01:27:06.253
"Myself."

01:27:11.359 --> 01:27:14.695
Who else has seen this?

01:27:14.697 --> 01:27:16.697
No one.

01:27:17.832 --> 01:27:19.533
Why not?

01:27:19.535 --> 01:27:19.967
'Cause...

01:27:19.969 --> 01:27:24.705
Adam, do you think that anyone would have thought twice

01:27:24.707 --> 01:27:26.440
about the way they treated him

01:27:26.442 --> 01:27:28.475
if they never had to think that it might have been

01:27:28.477 --> 01:27:31.712
one of us who killed him?

01:27:40.021 --> 01:27:43.557
They did kill him.

01:27:43.559 --> 01:27:45.659
Exactly.

01:27:46.894 --> 01:27:49.997
Now do you understand...

01:27:52.934 --> 01:27:54.968
I was only trying to help.

01:27:54.970 --> 01:27:57.504
Who says I need fixing?

01:28:00.875 --> 01:28:04.878
Jamie, what is this?

01:28:06.648 --> 01:28:08.048
That's mine.

01:28:08.050 --> 01:28:08.882
She had no right!

01:28:08.884 --> 01:28:10.350
(Gracie) I didn't mean to take it.

01:28:10.352 --> 01:28:12.753
- I didn't... I found it.
- Ssh!

01:28:14.389 --> 01:28:18.825
Really doesn't matter, Adam, not anymore.

01:28:19.694 --> 01:28:24.698
Don't you see, we can make this work.

01:28:24.700 --> 01:28:27.301
Make what work?

01:28:33.841 --> 01:28:35.042
This.

01:28:35.044 --> 01:28:37.878
Me and you.

01:28:37.880 --> 01:28:39.446
Well, we can't... I can't.

01:28:39.448 --> 01:28:43.884
Don't listen to her, Adam!

01:28:43.886 --> 01:28:45.719
She's just jealous.

01:28:45.721 --> 01:28:46.386
Jealous.

01:28:46.388 --> 01:28:50.724
Jamie, listen to me, you gotta calm down.

01:28:54.362 --> 01:28:58.565
You have to go.

01:28:58.567 --> 01:28:59.700
Just drop it.

01:28:59.702 --> 01:29:00.801
Drop the whole thing.

01:29:00.803 --> 01:29:02.969
I will not drop it!

01:29:02.971 --> 01:29:04.838
And you're right, I don't understand.

01:29:04.840 --> 01:29:07.341
But I know that I can't change what happened to you...

01:29:07.343 --> 01:29:10.544
You don't know anything about...

01:29:10.546 --> 01:29:13.513
(Muttering) It’s over...

01:29:16.384 --> 01:29:19.519
Just come home.

01:29:19.521 --> 01:29:21.922
Come home, Adam.

01:29:21.924 --> 01:29:22.522
We can...

01:29:22.524 --> 01:29:24.458
Stop telling me what to do!

01:29:24.460 --> 01:29:26.093
Stop hanging around my closet,

01:29:26.095 --> 01:29:27.961
and stop taking my words!

01:29:27.963 --> 01:29:28.895
Jamie, Adam can't fix...

01:29:28.897 --> 01:29:29.963
This has nothing to do with you!

01:29:29.965 --> 01:29:31.031
What happened to you was awful,

01:29:31.033 --> 01:29:34.568
but that does not mean you can come into our lives...

01:29:34.570 --> 01:29:35.702
(Shouting)

01:29:35.704 --> 01:29:39.606
Stop it!

01:29:39.608 --> 01:29:41.875
Jamie, Jamie!

01:29:41.877 --> 01:29:43.610
Listen to me!

01:29:43.612 --> 01:29:46.947
Is this how you want me to remember you?

01:29:46.949 --> 01:29:48.815
Look at me.

01:29:48.817 --> 01:29:51.752
'Cause that's not what I want.

01:29:54.689 --> 01:29:58.158
You don't know what you did.

01:29:58.160 --> 01:30:00.894
You didn't do it.

01:30:00.896 --> 01:30:02.429
Let me go.

01:30:02.431 --> 01:30:04.831
Leave me alone!

01:30:23.751 --> 01:30:27.154
Do you want me to come with you?

01:30:41.702 --> 01:30:45.639
♪♪

01:30:58.686 --> 01:31:02.556
(Crying)

01:31:13.634 --> 01:31:17.537
You don't have to go there alone.

01:31:29.050 --> 01:31:31.551
(Door closing)

01:31:39.794 --> 01:31:43.497
(Jamie) Thanks for coming, Gracie.

01:31:44.832 --> 01:31:46.700
And...

01:31:46.702 --> 01:31:50.604
I'm sorry about your rock collection.

01:31:52.740 --> 01:31:55.909
It wasn't really mine anyways.

01:31:56.644 --> 01:31:59.913
I'm sorry that I took your list.

01:32:02.149 --> 01:32:04.851
That's okay.

01:32:18.266 --> 01:32:21.234
Let's go.

01:32:22.136 --> 01:32:26.206
♪♪

01:32:58.873 --> 01:33:02.976
You don't have to wait, Gracie.

01:33:02.978 --> 01:33:04.144
Are you sure?

01:33:04.146 --> 01:33:07.013
How will you get home?

01:33:07.015 --> 01:33:09.082
I'm sure.

01:33:40.915 --> 01:33:44.084
(Jamie) You could come with me.

01:33:48.990 --> 01:33:51.992
Hey.

01:33:55.796 --> 01:33:59.799
Everything's gonna be all right.

01:33:59.801 --> 01:34:01.968
I know, I know.

01:34:01.970 --> 01:34:04.971
I'll see you again.

01:34:11.145 --> 01:34:15.815
You'll be fine too, you know?

01:34:15.817 --> 01:34:17.283
Yeah, I know.

01:34:19.320 --> 01:34:22.822
I got something for you.

01:34:29.430 --> 01:34:31.931
Love.

01:34:45.179 --> 01:34:48.882
Tell that to Gracie for me too, okay?

01:34:51.018 --> 01:34:53.153
I will.

01:35:07.902 --> 01:35:10.403
Here.

01:35:13.340 --> 01:35:16.309
Remember me.

01:35:25.753 --> 01:35:28.822
I'm glad it was you, Adam.

01:35:32.259 --> 01:35:35.228
Me too, Jamie.

01:35:36.931 --> 01:35:39.299
Me too.

